trong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML 缩写元素</strong>（<strong><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code></strong>）用于代表缩写，并且可以通过可选的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a> 属性提供完整的描述。若使用 <code>title</code> 属性，则它必须且仅可包含完整的描述内容。</p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"375\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/tabbed/abbr.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>这篇文章： <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/HTML/Howto/Mark_abbreviations_and_make_them_understandable\">How to mark abbreviations and make them understandable</a></em> 是一份学习使用 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 与其他相关元素的指南。</p>\n<table class=\"properties\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Content categories (en-US)</a></th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Flow content (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">phrasing content (en-US)</a>, palpable content</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Permitted content</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Phrasing content (en-US)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Tag omission</th>\n      <td>不允许，开始标签和结束标签都不能省略。</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Permitted parents</th>\n      <td>Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">phrasing content (en-US)</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">Permitted ARIA roles</th>\n      <td>Any</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th scope=\"row\">DOM Interface</th>\n      <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p>这个元素只有<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">全局属性</a>。在同 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 元素一起使用的时候，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a> 属性有特殊的语法含义; 它必须包含对一个缩写完全天然可读的扩写或者描述。这些文本通常会作为提示，在鼠标指针覆盖到该元素时显示作为一个提示。</p>\n<p>你使用的每一个 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 元素与其它同类元素都是相互独立的，为其中一个提供 <code>title</code> 不会自动把相同的附加文字依附到其它内容文字相同的元素上。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法注解","title":"用法注解","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"典型使用场景","title":"典型使用场景","isH3":true,"content":"<p>当然，我们不是所有的缩写都要使用<code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code>标记。但是其在下面一些场景很有帮助：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>当你想为缩写在文档流外提供一段扩展或定义的时候，为 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 设置一个合适的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a>。</li>\n  <li>在定义一个读者可能不太熟悉的缩写时，使用 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 和<code>title</code>属性或内联的文本来表现这个术语。</li>\n  <li>当文本中出现需要进行语义上的标注的缩写词时，<code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code>元素可用于依次将其作用样式和脚本。</li>\n  <li>可以将 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 与 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a> 配合使用来建立缩写或首字母缩略词的定义。 请参阅下面的示例 <a href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%BC%A9%E5%86%99\">定义一个缩写</a>。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法注意事项","title":"语法注意事项","isH3":true,"content":"<p>在有 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%95%E5%A4%8D%E6%95%B0\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">单复数</a> 的语言中（即物体数量会影响句子语法的语言）， <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 元素和其中的 <code>title</code> 属性应当单复数一致。这在阿拉伯语这样超过二数的语言中非常重要，在英语中也有一定的影响。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"默认样式","title":"默认样式","isH3":false,"content":"<p>虽然完全为了网站制作者的方便，所有的浏览器都默认把这个元素显示为行内元素 (<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/display\"><code>display</code></a><code>: inline</code>) ，但是默认样式在不同浏览器中存在差别：</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>一些浏览器，比如 IE，对它的添加的样式和<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a> 元素的样式完全相同。</li>\n  <li>Opera、Firefox 和其他一些浏览器给这个元素的内容添加一条点状下划线 。</li>\n  <li>一些浏览器不仅添加点状下划线，而且还把元素的内容添加小写大写字母的样式。若要避免这种样式，在 CSS 中添加 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/font-variant\"><code>font-variant</code></a><code>: none</code> 。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"创建语义化的缩写","title":"创建语义化的缩写","isH3":true,"content":"<p>想要创建不含解释或描述性的缩写，就直接用<code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code>不添加任何属性。请看下面的例子。</p>\n<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Using <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>HTML<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> is fun and easy!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"结果\">结果</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"创建语义化的缩写\" id=\"frame_marking_up_an_abbreviation_semantically\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr/_sample_.marking_up_an_abbreviation_semantically.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"缩写样式","title":"缩写样式","isH3":true,"content":"<p>你可以像这个简单的例子一样，用 CSS 来为缩写做一个样式。</p>\n<h4 id=\"html_2\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Using <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>CSS<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>, you can style your abbreviations!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"css\">CSS</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">abbr</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-variant</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> all-small-caps<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"result\">Result</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"缩写样式\" id=\"frame_styling_abbreviations\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr/_sample_.styling_abbreviations.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"提供扩展","title":"提供扩展","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Adding a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a> attribute lets you provide an expansion or definition for the abbreviation or acronym.</p>\n<p>添加一个 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes#attr-title\"><code>title</code></a> 属性，为缩写提供定义或拓展。</p>\n<h4 id=\"html_3\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Ashok's joke made me <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Laugh Out Loud<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>LOL<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> big\ntime.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"结果_2\">结果</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"提供扩展\" id=\"frame_providing_an_expansion\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr/_sample_.providing_an_expansion.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"定义一个缩写","title":"定义一个缩写","isH3":true,"content":"<p>You can use <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> in tandem with <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a> to more formally define an abbreviation, as shown here.</p>\n<p><code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 与 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a> 联合使用可以定义一个更加正式的缩写，如下：</p>\n<h4 id=\"html_4\">HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dfn</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>html<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>HyperText Markup Language<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>HTML<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dfn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> is a markup language used to create the semantics and structure\nof a web page.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>A <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dfn</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>spec<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Specification<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dfn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n(<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">title</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Specification<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>spec<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>) is a document that outlines\nin detail how a technology or API is intended to function and how it is\naccessed.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"结果_3\">结果</h4><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"定义一个缩写\" id=\"frame_defining_an_abbreviation\" width=\"600\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr/_sample_.defining_an_abbreviation.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>可以在 <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Advanced_text_formatting#abbreviations\">How to mark abbreviations and make them understandable</a></em> 中浏览更多深层次的实例。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"无障碍问题","title":"无障碍问题","isH3":false,"content":"<p>在缩略词第一次出现在页面的时候，将它书写完整对帮助人们理解很有用处的，特别是内容是技术或者工业术语</p>\n<h4 id=\"example\">Example</h4>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>JavaScript Object Notation (<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>JSON<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>abbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>) is a lightweight data-interchange format.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>这对于不熟悉内容中讨论的术语或概念的人，对语言不熟悉的人以及具有认知问题的人特别有用。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-abbr-element","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"html.elements.abbr"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.abbr","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML/Advanced_text_formatting#%e7%bc%a9%e7%95%a5%e8%af%ad\">高级文字格式 - 使用 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 元素</a></li>\n  <li>其他传达文本级语义的元素：<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\"><code>&lt;a&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\"><code>&lt;em&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\"><code>&lt;cite&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\"><code>&lt;q&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\"><code>&lt;dfn&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\"><code>&lt;code&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\"><code>&lt;kbd&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\"><code>&lt;b&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\"><code>&lt;i&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/mark\"><code>&lt;mark&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rp\"><code>&lt;rp&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\"><code>&lt;bdo&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\"><code>&lt;br&gt;</code></a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a>.</li>\n  <li>已被弃用的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/acronym\"><code>&lt;acronym&gt;</code></a> 元素，原被用于展示首字母缩写。其作用被归入了 <code>&lt;abbr&gt;</code> 的作用中。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"用法注解","id":"用法注解"},{"text":"默认样式","id":"默认样式"},{"text":"例子","id":"例子"},{"text":"无障碍问题","id":"无障碍问题"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"HTML 缩写元素（<abbr>）用于代表缩写，并且可以通过可选的 title 属性提供完整的描述。若使用 title 属性，则它必须且仅可包含完整的描述内容。","popularity":0.0005,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<abbr>: The Abbreviation element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<abbr>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<abbr> : l'élément d'abréviation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<abbr>: 略語要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<abbr>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<abbr>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<abbr>: Элемент Аббревиатура","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/html/element/abbr","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/html/element/abbr/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML（超文本标记语言）"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"HTML 元素参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr","title":"<abbr>"}],"pageTitle":"<abbr> - HTML（超文本标记语言） | MDN","noIndexing":false}}